      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You need a free hand to properly use a breakaway aegis; you can hold an item in that hand but not use it or makeattacks with it. As a reaction, when you are hit by a melee attack from an opponent you can perceive, you can use the aegis to absorb some of the blow. This negates 5 damage but causes the aegis to crumble into its component pieces. The aegis is useless until you gather up the parts and spend 10 minutes putting them back together.</p>"
